@startuml sequence_zapping_liba4tv_v2
title Zapping v2 - Comedia javni API (gore) + PDF sablon Platforme/HAL ispod Comedije (demonstration)
' Sabloni: Module 5 Fig.3, Module 6 Fig.2/3 (platform/HAL), Fig.4 (tune) i Fig.5 (A/V playback), Module 3 (PCR/PTS), Module 7 Fig.5

actor User
box "Android app" #EBF5FF
  participant "Live TV App" as App
  participant "Broadcast TvInputService" as TIS
end box
box "Comedia - iWedia liba4tv" #E8F5E9
  participant "ComediaRouteManagerControl" as ROUTE
  participant "DisplayControl" as DISP
  participant "ServiceControl" as SVC
  participant "Comedia CHAL - TDAL" as CHAL
end box
box "Ispod Comedije - Platform i HAL - demonstration" #FFF3E0
  participant "Tuner SDK / Tuner HAL" as TSDK
  participant "MediaCodec / AudioTrack" as AVDEC
end box

User -> App : Play channel 1
App -> TIS : onSetSurface(surface)
App -> TIS : onSetStreamVolume(0.0)
App -> TIS : onTune(channelUri)
TIS -> ROUTE : getLiveRoute(listIndex, serviceIndex, prevRouteId)
ROUTE --> TIS : liveRoute
TIS -> DISP : setVideoSurface(layer, SurfaceBundle)
TIS -> SVC : registerListener(serviceListener)
TIS -> SVC : startServiceByTriplet(liveRoute, listIndex, serviceIndex, onid, tsid, sid)
note over SVC,CHAL : startServiceByTriplet je ASINHRON; Comedia interno: live route -> CHAL (TDAL)

SVC -> CHAL : pokreni playback na ruti
CHAL -> TSDK : tune izvor + otvori A/V + PCR PID filtere
note over TSDK : demonstration: frontend tune + demux PID filteri\nkomunicira sa HAL (TUNER/DEMUX) -> Nexus/Magnum (ref. Module 6 Fig.4 i Fig.5)
CHAL -> AVDEC : dekoduj video + audio; PCR/STC sync (lipsync)
note over AVDEC : demonstration: video+audio dekoder + display\nkomunicira sa HAL (VDEC/ADEC/GPU) (ref. Module 6 Fig.5; Module 3 PCR/PTS)
AVDEC --> CHAL : A/V tece, sinhronizovano
CHAL --> SVC : komponente spremne (PCR PID)

SVC --> TIS : ServiceListener.channelChangeStatus(liveRoute, true, ServiceStateChangeError.OK)
SVC --> TIS : ServiceListener.safeToUnblank(liveRoute)
TIS -> App : unmute (restore volume) + video vidljiv
TIS -> SVC : getServiceDescriptor(listIndex, serviceIndex)
SVC --> TIS : ServiceDescriptor (getName, getONID, getTSID, getServiceId)
TIS --> App : Service started -> Playback active
@enduml
